{"tid":955013,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"其實男仔送女仔返屋企真係必然？","createTime":"2018-12-25T05:35:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-25T08:34:40.000Z","uid":190962,"like":30,"dislike":44,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"904d71e7ba34dd19e592f8198580da312bc50869","tid":955013,"uid":190962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T05:35:27.000Z","msg":"住得近送都還可以嘅，但係如果住得遠仲要送嘅話個男仔好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n出咗成日街已經夠攰，而且要送完條女返屋企之後仲要趕尾班車。如果唔好彩冇尾班車仲要俾返百幾蚊的士錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  其實大家各行各路可能仲可以早啲返到去做自己嘢<br />\n<br />\n大家係prefer送個女仔返屋企/比人送返去？<br />\n定唔送/唔被送唔想麻煩到人？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  唔送，因為大家有手有腳有眼耳口鼻，咁大個人識自己返<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 送啊，有風度返少少啊嘛，一個女仔好危險<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cdc87078e8c959d9e8e7ab292a456d80a67b1f6","tid":955013,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T05:37:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d68712672918908ba3fdd0bc8c9a8f1a40733c19","tid":955013,"uid":196924,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T05:42:23.000Z","msg":"識過個啦<br />\n我尋晚由將軍澳去到屯門都係7個字<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac7368b6e4bd4168256c1179dacb77fb9baed134","tid":955013,"uid":80792,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T05:42:42.000Z","msg":"想見耐d"},{"pid":"6ead289993a9fcd783fb1c1c96547bb658024811","tid":955013,"uid":118989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T05:45:22.000Z","msg":"男人老狗送男人返屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5516b96814f2f365c823ca844207903e725940f6","tid":955013,"uid":190962,